node.text:
My @remington.college #culinaryarts students & I really enjoyed making my🍒”Grilled Cherry Galletini” together! swipe for recipe from @indulgebykathywakile
Side note: you can substitute chèvre for cream cheese & rosemary for your favorite herb, I used basil in this case! Also can be baked in the oven as well! I like options! Enjoy served with your favorite vanilla ice cream! 
#eatliveloveindulge #remingtoncollege #memphis #kwrealculinarykitchen

Also I've just been feeling overall so rejuvenated and fresh! Use my code KATHY for 20% off!! #thankyouteami #Teamiblends
